gov.nasa.arc.mct.components
Class ExtendedProperties

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.arc.mct.components.ExtendedProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class ExtendedProperties
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable

This class contains the set of properties for a specific view. Each property is a pair of type and each set of properties is associated with one component only. Each set of properties will be shared across a cluster of MCT if the owner component is shared; therefore, each method of this class will need to be synchronized to obtain the proper cluster-wide monitor. The APIs of this class is only accessible from the package of the AbstractViewRole.
